ResumesGenerator is a dynamic resume creation website designed to help users build their own resumes easily. With the ability to add or remove sections, users have full control over their content. The platform offers three unique templates, and while it's currently free, premium features will be introduced in the future.

Features:

Dynamic resume creation with editable sections.
Three customizable templates.
Free to use, with plans for a paid version.
Technologies:

Backend: PHP, Laravel, Livewire
Frontend: Tailwind CSS, Alpine.js
Setup Instructions:

Clone the repository: git clone [repository URL]
Install dependencies: composer install && npm install
Migrate the database: php artisan migrate
Serve the application: php artisan serve
